title: DataCore SANsymphony: Hosts
agents: datacore_rest
catalog: storage/datacore
license: GPLv2
distribution: andre_eckstein
description:
 This check monitors SAN client hosts connected to a DataCore SANsymphony
 storage system. These are the servers that access virtual disks through
 FC or iSCSI connections.

 The check monitors host status, connection state, and displays information
 about client ports and mapped virtual disks.

 This check requires the special agent configurable through
 "DataCore SANsymphony via REST API".

item:
 The name (Alias or Caption) of the host.

discovery:
 One service is created for each connected host.
